                    <span>honestly its been three or more years since i read this burgett book, but it only took me two days to finish it. it just sucks you in and im a very slow reader. burgett is very matter of fact about his training and war time experiences.  from training accidents to killing men so badly burned there was no alternative to relieving them of their suffering. truley powerful.</span>
                  
